OL,3,CMan banned from every Tesco in UK
OL,4,Cafter shoplifting conviction
OL,6,FA prolific thief has been banned from
OL,7,Fevery Tesco, Tesco Express, Home
OL,8,FBargains and Spar store in the country
OL,9,Fafter he was convicted of shoplifting
OL,10,Fat Preston Magistrates Court.
OL,12,FMagistrates gave 42-year-old John
OL,13,FMolyneux, of Greenwood in Bamber
OL,14,FBridge a Criminal Behaviour Order
OL,15,F(CBO) as a result of the offences, and
OL,16,Fhe must comply with it for two years
OL,17,Ffollowing his appearance in court.
