OL,4,Cafter shoplifting conviction
OL,6,FIt prohibits him from entering any
OL,7,FTesco, Tesco Express, Home Bargains or
OL,8,FSpar in the country as well as
OL,9,FThorntons on Hough Lane in Leyland,
OL,10,Fand Gee Tees on Station Road in Bamber
OL,11,FBridge.
OL,13,FCourt documents indicate that Molyneux
OL,14,Fwas brought to court after pleading
OL,15,Fguilty to stealing #50 worth of meat
OL,16,Fproducts from Asda in Leyland on 3
OL,17,FMarch.
OL,19,FHe also admitted failing to surrender
OL,20,Finto custody on 22 April having been
OL,21,Freleased on bail on 25 March.
