OL,3,CMan banned from every Tesco in UK
OL,4,Cafter shoplifting conviction
OL,6,FIn a statement, Lancashire
OL,7,FConstabulary said: "Operation Vulture
OL,8,Fis Lancashire Constabulary's response
OL,9,Fto shoplifting across the county,
OL,10,Fbacked by Lancashire's Police and
OL,11,FCrime Commissioner Clive Grunshaw.
OL,13,F"The operation sees dedicated officers
OL,14,Fundertaking hotspot patrolling,
OL,15,Fincreasing their visibility in
OL,16,Ftargeted areas and creating strong
OL,17,Fpartnerships with retailers across the
OL,18,Fcounty to better share intelligence,
OL,19,Fget a deeper understanding of retail
OL,20,Fcrime and identify more offenders."
